I wanted to sincerely thank you Jeff. I feel like I am in a darkest moment of my life. I study abroad (like 24h flight from my country). I didn't see my wife for half of a year. I didn't see the rest of my family for two years already. My boss keeps on pushing me further and further. I'm out of money. Basically speaking, the only thing that keeps me together is working out. I follow your videos. I lost 12kg of body fat, yet every friend I meet thinks I'm two times bigger then I was. I changed my habits. I eat healthier then ever. Thank you.
PS. I also love community surrounding you. Whenever I'm down, I just open your video and read the comments.
PSS. If I will ever visit USA (what is quite possible, because a lot of great scientific conferences are there) I will drive through the whole country and ask for yours and Jessie's autographs.

I wanted to sincerely thank you Jeff. I feel like I am in a darkest moment of my life. I study abroad (like 24h flight from my country). I didn't see my wife for half of a year. I didn't see the rest of my family for two years already. My boss keeps on pushing me further and further. I'm out of money.  Basically speaking, the only thing that keeps me together is working out. I follow your videos. I lost 12kg of body fat, yet every friend I meet thinks I'm two times bigger then I was. I changed my habits. I eat healthier then ever. Thank you.
PS. I also love community surrounding you. Whenever I'm down, I just open your video and read the comments.
PSS. If I will ever visit USA (what is quite possible, because a lot of great scientific conferences are there) I will drive through the whole country and ask for yours and Jessie's autographs.
